hadiths[62]{hadithnumber,text}:
627,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke jab musalman Madina aaye to wo ikhattey hotey aur namaz key waqt ka andaza lagatey they. koi shakhs us (namaz) ka aelan na karta tha. eik din unhoney is masley key barey mein baat cheet ki. chunanche kisi ney kaha : esaiyon jaisa naaqoos (ghantaa) bana lo. kisi ney kaha : balke yahudiyon jaisa narsinghaa (dhutu) bana lo. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : tum (namaz key waqt) koi aadmi (galiyon mein) kyon nahin bhej detey jo namaz ka aelan kerey. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal ! utho aur namaz ka aelan karo.
628,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke Azan key kalimaat do do baar kahin aur iqaamat key kalimaat eik eik baar.
629,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein Azan key kalimaat do do baar they aur iqaamat (takbir) key eik eik baar magar ye ke to (قد قامت الصلاۃ) (do martaba) kahey."
630,"Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein (apney paas) bithaya aur harf ba harf (eik eik kalima kar key) Azan. sikhlaai (Hadees key raawi) Ibrahim ney kaha ke wo bilkul hamari Azan ki tarah thi. (bashar bin Muaz kehtey hain ke) mainey un sey kaha : zara mujhey suna do. to unhoney kaha : (اللہ اکبر ، اللہ اکبر) do baar, (أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ) do baar, (أشھد أن محمدًا رسول اللہ) do baar, phir is sey mukhtalif (buland) aawaz key sath kaha jo ird-gird key logon ko sunai deti thi : (أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ) do baar,(أشھد أن محمدًا رسول اللہ) do baar, (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ) do baar, (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح) do baar, (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر), (لا الہ الا اللہ)."
631,"Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey Azan mein unnis (19) kalimaat aur iqaamat mein satrah (17) kalimaat sikhaey, phir Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ney unnis (19) aur satarah (17) kalimaat shumar kiye."
632,"Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mujhey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Azan sikhlaai aur farmaya : (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر), ''Allah sab sey bada hai.'' (أشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ), ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin.'' (أشھد أن محمدا رسول اللہ ، أشھدا أن محمدا رسول اللہ),''main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain.'' phir dobara kahey : (أشھد أن لا الہ الا االلہ ، أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ ، أشھد أن محمدا رسول اللہ ، أشھد أن محمدا رسول اللہ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ),''namaz key liye aa'o, namaz key liye aa'o.""(حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح), kamiyabi key liye aa'o, kamiyabi key liye aa'o.''(اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر),''Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai.'' (لا الہ الا اللہ)''Allah key siwa koi bar-haq mabood nahin.''"
633,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Muheereez sey riwayat hai … … wo yatim they aur unhoney Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ki god mein parwarish pai thi yahan tak ke khud Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein Sham ki taraf tayyar kar key bheja. unhoney farmaya : mainey (Shaam aatey waqt) Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora sey guzarish ki ke main Sham ja raha hun aur mujhey ummid hai ke wahan mujh sey aap ki Azan key barey mein puchha jaeyga (aap mujhey kuchh bata dijiye). to Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke main kuchh logon key sath nikla. hum Hunain key raastey mein they ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hunain sey wapis tashrif laye aur aap raastey hi mein hamein miley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan ney aap ki mojudgi mein namaz ki Azan kahi. hum aap sey kuchh door they. hamney muazzan ki aawaz suni to hum un ki naqal utaarney lagey aur mazaq karney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney wo aawaz sun li to aap ney hamein bulwaya yahan tak ke hum aap key samney khadey ho gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey wo kon hai jiski buland aawaz mainey suni hai? merey sathiyon ney meri taraf ishara kiya aur unhoney sach kaha. aap ney un sab ko chhod diya aur mujhey thehra liya aur farmaya : utho namaz ki Azan kaho. main utha to Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khud mujhey Azan sikhai. aap ney farmaya : kaho : (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ), phir aap ney farmaya : apni aawaz buland karo aur dobara kaho : (اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح ، اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، لا الہ الا اللہ),phir jab mainey Azan mukammal kar li to aap ney mujhey bulaya aur eik thaili di jis mein kuchh chaandi thi. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey Makka Mukarrama main Azan par muqarrar farma dijiye. aap ney farmaya : mainey tumhein muqarrar kar diya. to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key muqarrar kiye huye Makka ke governer Hazrat Itaab bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey governer key samney Azan kehta raha."
634,"Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Hunain (ki wadi) sey nikley hum Makka waley das ladkey un (musalmanon) ki talash mein nikley. hamney unhein suna, wo namaz ki Azan keh rahey they. hum bhi khadey ho kar unhein mazaq kartey huye Azan kehney lagey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey un mein sey eik achchhi aawaz waley ladkey ki aawaz suni hai. so aap ney hamein bula bheja. hum mein sey har eik ney baari baari Azan kahi. main sab sey aakhir mein tha. jab mainey Azan kahi to aap ney farmaya : idhar aa'o. aur mujhey apney samney bitha liya aur meri peshani par haath pherney lagey aur teen dafa merey liye barkat ki dua ki. phir farmaya : jaao Baitullah key paas Azan kaha karo. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kaisey (Azan kahun)? to aap ney mujhey Azan siklaai jaisa ke tum ab kehtey ho : (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح),aur subah ki pehli Azan mein (الصلاۃ خیر من النوم ، الصلاۃ خیر من النوم),''namaz neend sey behtar hai.'' unhoney kaha : aap ney mujhey iqaamat dohrai sikhaai, (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، اشھد ان محمدا رسول اللہ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح ، قد قامت الصلاۃ ، قد قامت الصلاۃ),namaz khadi ho gaee, namaz khadi ho gaee, (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، لا الہ الا اللہ). ibn Juraij bayan kartey hain ke mujhey ye hadees Usman bin Saaib ney apney walid aur Abdul-Malik bin Abu-Mahzoora ki walida sey bayan ki hai aur un dono ney ye hadees khud Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) sey suni hai."
635,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main aur mera chacha zaad bhai aur eik baar farmaya : main aur mera eik sathi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. (wapsi key waqt) aap ney farmaya : jab tum safar karo to Azan aur iqaamat kaha karo aur (jamaat key waqt) tum mein sey bada imaamat karaaey."
636,"Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur hum sab key sab nojawan hum umr they. hum aap key paas bees raaten thehrey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) badey reham karney waley aur nihayat naram dil they. aap ney mehsus farmaya ke hum ko ghar walon ka ishtiyaq ho gaya hai to aap ney hum sey puchha ke tum kin kin ko ghar chhod kar aaye ho? hum sab ney (apney apney hisab sey) aap ko bataya. aap ney farmaya : tum apney ghar baar ki taraf lot jao, unkey paas raho, unhein taalim do aur unhein Islaami ehkam batlaao. jab namaz ka waqt aaye to tum mein sey eik aadmi Azan kahe aur bada jamaat karaaey."
637,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub sey riwayat hai ke mujhey pehley ye riwayat Abu-Qulaba ney Hazrat Amr bin Salma sey bayan ki, phir Abu-Qulaba kehney lagey ke Amr bin Salma (Raziallahu anhu) zinda hain tum un sey mil kyon nahin letey ! Ayub ney kaha : main un sey ja kar mila aur un sey puchha to unhoney kaha ke jab fateh Makka ka waqiyaa huwa to har qom ney apney aeilane Islam main eik doosrey sey sabqat ki koshish ki. merey walid mohtaram bhi hamari basti walon key Islam ka aelan karney key liye aap key paas hazir huye. jab wo wapis aaye to hum unkey istaqbal key liye gaey ! unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main tumharey paas Allah Taala key sachchey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey aa raha hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : falan namaz falan waqt padho aur falan namaz falan waqt aur jab namaz ka waqt ho jaey to tum mein sey eik aadmi Azan kahe aur jo ziyada Quran padha huwa hai wo imaamat kerey."
638,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) raat ko Azan kehtey hain, lihaza tum khaatey, peetey rehna yahan tak ke Abdullah bin Ummey Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) Azan kahen."
639,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq Bilal raat ko Azan kehtey hain, lihaza khatey peetey raho yahan tak ke tum ibne Ummey Maktoom ki Azan suno."
640,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab Bilal Azan kahin to khatey peetey raho yahan tak ke ibn Ummey Maktoom Azan den. aur in dono azaanon key darmiyan sirf itna fasla hota tha ke eik utarta aur doosra chadh jata tha.
641,"Hazrat Unaisa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ibne Ummey Maktoom Azan kahin to tum khatey peetey raho aur jab Bilal Azan kahin to khana peena band kar do."
642,"Hazrat ibne Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq Bilal raat ko Azan kehtey hain taake soney waley ko jagaaey aur qiyam karney waley ko qiyam sey lautaaein (taake wo kuchh aaram kar ley) aur subah saadiq aisi nahin hoti (jaisi Bilal ki Azan key waqt hoti hai)."
643,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey subah key waqt key barey mein puchha to aap ney (pehley din) Bilal ko hukm diya. unhoney Azan kahi jun'hi Fajr tulu hui. jab aglaa din huwa to aap ney Fajr ki namaz ko muakhkhar (der) kiya yahan tak ke khub roshni ho gaee, phir aap ney unhein hukm diya to unhoney iqaamat kahi, phir aap ney namaz padhaai. phir farmaya : ye hai namaz subah ka waqt (yani kal aur aaj ki namazon key darmiyan)."
644,"Hazrat Abu Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bahar nikley aur Azan kahi. wo apni Azan mein aisey daeyn, baain munh modtey they."
645,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abu Sasaa Ansari sey kaha : tehqiq main dekhta hun ke tum bakriyon aur sehra key dildaada ho, is liye jab tum apni bakriyon aur sehra mein ho aur tum Azan kaho to buland aawaz sey Azan kaha karo, is liye ke muazzan ki aawaz ki inteha tak jo bhi jin aur insan ya koi aur chiz isey sunti hai, qiyamat key din uskey liye gawahi deygi. Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey ye baat Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai."
646,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key munh mubarak sey suna, aap farma rahey they : muazzan ki bakhshish ki jati hai jahan tak uski ( Azan ki ) aawaz pahunchey aur har khushk aur tar chiz (jandaar aur be-jaan) uskey liye gawahi deygi."
647,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tehqiq Allah Taala pehli saf par khususi rahmatein nazil farmata hai aur uskey farishtey rehmat ki dua kartey hain aur muazzan key uski aawaz pahunchney ki jagah tak key gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain aur uski Azan sunney wali har jandaar aur be-jaan chiz uskey eman ki tasdeeq keregi. aur usey uskey sath mil kar namaz padhney walon key barabar sawab milega."
648,Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey Azan kaha karta tha aur main Fajr ki pehli Azan mein (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح) key baad (الصلاۃ خیر من النوم ، الصلاۃ خیر من النوم ، اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، لا الہ الا اللہ) kaha karta tha.
649,Hazrat Sufiyan ki ye hadees isi sanad key sath hamein Amr bin Ali key wastey sey bhi pahunchi hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : (sanad mein mazkur Hazrat Sufiyan key ustaad) Abu-Jafar sey 'Abu-Jafar Faraa' murad nahin.
650,Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Azan key aakhiri kalimaat (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، لا الہ الا اللہ) hain.
651,Hazrat Aswad sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki Azan key aakhiri kalimaat (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر ، لا الہ الا اللہ) they.
652,Hazrat Ibrahim Nakh'i ki ye riwayat Aa'mash key wastey sey bhi hum tak pahunchi hai.
653,Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Azan ka aakhiri kalima  (لا الہ الا اللہ) hai.
654,banu Saqeef key eik aadmi sey riwayat hai ke us ney dorane safar mein barish wali raat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan ko yun kehtey suna : (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ ، حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح ، صلوا فی رحالکم) yani padhi. apney khemon mein namaz padh lo.
655,"Imam Naafey (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney thandi hawa wali raat mein Azan kahi to farmaya : (الا صلوا فی الرحال) khabrdar ! gharon mein namaz padh lo. kyonkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) muazzan ko hukm detey, jab barish wali thandi raat hoti ke wo (Azan mein) kahe : (الا صلوا فی الرحال)"
656,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) chaley yahan tak ke arfa mein aaye to wahan wadi namra mein apney liye khema laga huwa paya, chunanche aap is mein utrey yahan tak ke jab suraj dhal gaya to aap ney hukm diya, (aap ki oontni) qaswaa par paalaan kasa gaya. jab aap wadi namra key nasheb (dhalaan) mein pahunchey to logon ko khutba diya, phir Bilal ney Azan kahi phir iqaamat kahi to aap ney Zohar ki namaz padhaai phir iqaamat kahi to Asr ki namaz padhaai aur unkey darmiyan koi (nafl) namaz nahin padhi."
657,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (wapsi key doran mein) chaley yahan tak ke muzdalfa pahunch gaey. wahan Maghrib aur Isha ki namazein eik Azan aur do iqaamaton sey padhein aur unkey darmiyan nawaafil nahin padhey.
658,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke hum Muzdalfa mein Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key sath they. aap ney Azan kahi phir iqaamat kahi aur hamein Maghrib ki namaz padhaai phir farmaya : namaz key liye utho chunanche aap ney hamein Isha ki namaz do rakat padhaai. mainey kaha : ye kaisi namaz hai? farmaney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath is jagah aisey hi namaz padhi thi.
659,Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey marwi hai ke unhoney muzdalfa mein Maghrib aur Isha ki namazein eik iqaamat sey padhein phir unhoney Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bayan kiya ke unhoney aisey hi kiya tha aur Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi aisey hi kiya tha.
660,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath muzdalfa mein (Maghrib aur Isha ki) namazein eik iqaamat key sath padhein.
661,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muzdalfa mein Maghrib aur Isha ki namazein ikhatti padhi thin. aap ney un mein sey har namaz alag iqaamat sey padhi aur in mein kisi namaz sey bhi aagey ya peechey nafl nahin padhey.
662,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hamein mushrikon ney jange khandaq key din Zohar ki namaz sey masroof rakha yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya, ladaai (ki namaz) key barey mein jo kuch nazil huwa (yani namaze khof ka tareeqa) ye is sey pehley ki baat hai, chunanche Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaar di : (وکفی اللہ المومنین القتال), ''Allah taala mominon ko ladaai sey kafi ho gaya.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney Zohar ki namaz ki iqaamat kahi to aap ney is tarah namaz padhi jis tarah waqt mein padha kartey they, phir Asr ki iqaamat kahi to aap ney wo namaz bhi isi tarah padhi jis tarah waqt mein padha kartey they, phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney Maghrib ki Azan kahi to aap ney isey uskey waqt mein padha."
663,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke tehqiq mushrekin ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko jange khandaq main eik din chaar namazon sey rokey rakha. aap ney Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya to unhoney Azan kahi phir iqaamat kahi chunanche aap ney Zohar ki namaz padhi, phir iqaamat kahi to aap ney Asr ki namaz padhi, phir iqaamat kahi to aap ney Maghrib ki namaz padhi, phir iqaamat kahi to aap ney Isha ki namaz padhi."
664,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum eik jang mein they to mushrikon ney hamein Zohar, Asr, Maghrib aur Isha ki namazon sey rokey rakha. jab mushrekin peechhey hat gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muazzan ko hukm diya. us ney Zohar ki namaz key liye iqaamat kahi to hamney namaz padhi, phir us ney Asr ki namaz key liye iqaamat kahi to hamney Asr padhi, phir us ney Maghrib ki namaz key liye iqaamat kahi to hamney Maghrib ki namaz padhi, phir us ney Isha ki namaz key liye iqaamat kahi to hamney Isha ki namaz padhi, phir aap hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : roey-zameen par tumharey ilawa koi jamaat (is waqt ) Allah ka zikr nahin kar rahi."
665,Hazrat Muawiya bin Hudaij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik din namaz padhi aur salam pher diya (aur masjid sey bahar chaley gaey) halanke eik rakat baqi thi. eik aadmi peechhey sey ja kar aap ko mila aur batlaya ke aap eik rakat bhool gaey hain. aap dobara masjid mein dakhil huye aur Bilal ko hukm diya. unhoney iqaamat kahi to aap ney logon ko faut shuda rakat padhaai. mainey ye baat ja kar doosrey logon ko batlaai to unhoney mujh sey kaha : kya tum us aadmi ko pehchantey ho? mainey kaha nahin magar ye ke main unhein dobara dekhun. ittifaaq se wo merey paas sey guzrey to mainey kaha : ye hain woh. logon ney kaha : ye Talha bin Ubedullah hain.
666,Hazrat Abdullah bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap ney eik aadmi ki aawaz suni jo Azan keh raha tha. aap uski Azan ka jawab deney lagey. jab wo (أشھد أن محمداً رسول اللہ) tak pahuncha to aap ney farmaya : tehqiq ye shakhs bakriyon ka charwaahaa hai ya apney ghar walon sey bichhda huwa hai. phir aap us wadi mein utrey to pata chala ke wo bakriyon ka charwaahaa hai. aap eik mari hui bakri key paas sey guzrey. aap ney farmaya : tumhein yaqin hai ke ye bakri apney ghar walon key nazdik be-qadr hai? sahaba ney arz kiya : haan. aap ney farmaya : duniya Allah Taala key nazdik is (bakri) sey bhi badh kar zaleel hai.
667,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah Taala bakriyon key us charwahey sey tajjub karta hai jo kisi pahad ki choti par rehta hai aur Azan keh kar namaz padhta hai. Allah farmata hai : merey is bandey ko dekho. Azan kehta hai aur namaz qaaim karta hai. mujh sey darta hai. mainey apney bandey ko maaf kar diya aur usey jannat mein dakhil kar diya.
668,Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz ki saf mein bethey huye they-------- . (Al-hadees)
669,"Jaama' masjid key muazzan Abu-Musanna ney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey Azan key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein Azan do do kalimaat they aur iqaamat eik eik kalima magar jab tu (قد قامت الصلاۃ) kahe to wo do martaba hai. jab hum (قد قامت الصلاۃ) key alfaz suntey to wuzu kartey, phir namaz key liye jatey."
670,Hazrat Malik bin Huweris (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey aur merey sathi ko kaha : jab namaz ka waqt aaye to tum Azan kaho phir iqaamat kaho phir tum mein sey bada imaamat karwaaey.
671,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namaz key liye Azan kahi jati hai to shetan hawa chhodta (paadta) huwa bhaagtaa hai yahan tak ke Azan nahin sunta. jab Azan mukammal ho jati hai to aa jata hai, phir jab iqaamat kahi jati hai to phir bhag jata hai, yahan tak ke iqaamat mukammal ho jati hai to wapis aa jata hai, yahan tak ke aadmi aur uskey dil key darmiyan waswasey daalta hai, usey kehta hai : falan chiz yad kar, falan chiz yad kar. aisi cheezen jo pehley uskey zehen mein nahin thin yahan tak ke aadmi ki ye haalat ho jati hai ke wo nahin janta ke kitni namaz padhi hai?"
672,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar log Azan aur saf awwal ki fazilat ko jantey aur phir qura andazi key ilawa koi chaara kaar na paatey to inkey liye zarur qura andazi kartey. agar log Zohar ki namaz jaldi (awwal waqt mein) padhney ki fazilat jantey to eik dusrey sey aagey bhagtey aur agar Isha aur Fajr ki fazilat ko jantey to zarur aatey chahey (chaahey) ghisat kar hi aana padey."
673,Hazrat Usman bin Abul-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey guzarish ki ke aap mujhey meri qom ka Imam muqarrar farma den. aap ney farmaya : tum unkey Imam ho. namaz padhatey waqt un mein sey kamzor tareen aadmi ka lihaz rakhna aur aisa muazzan rakhna jo apni Azan par tankhwaah na leta ho.
674,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum Azan suno to isi tarah kaho jis tarah muazzan kehta hai."
675,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) khadey ho kar Azan kehney lagey. jab wo khamosh huye to aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney in kalmaat ki tarah kalimaat (jawaaban) kahe wo yaqinan jannat mein dakhil hoga.
676,Hazrat Majmaa bin Yahya Ansari ney kaha : main Hazrat Abu-Umama bin Sahal bin Hanif key paas betha tha ke muazzan ney Azan shuru kar di. us ney do baar (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر) kaha to aap ney bhi do baar (اللہ اکبر اللہ اکبر) kaha. phir us ney do baar (أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ) kaha to aap ney bhi do baar (أشھد أن لا الہ الا اللہ) kaha. phir us ney (أشھد أن محمداً رسول اللہ) kaha to aap ney bhi do martaba (أشھد أن محمداً رسول اللہ) kaha. phir farmaya : mujhey Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan Raziallahu anhuma ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman isi tarah bayan kiya.
677,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, jab ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muazzan ki Azan suni thi, ke aap is tarah farma rahey they jis tarah muazzan keh raha tha."
678,"Hazrat Alqama bin Waqas sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : tehqiq main Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas tha jab unkey muazzan ney Azan shuru ki. Hazrat Muawiya ney bhi isi tarah kaha jis tarah muazzan kehta tha yahan tak ke jab us ney (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلاۃ) kaha to aap ney (لا حول wala قوۃ الا باللہ) kaha, phir jab us ney (حی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الفلاح) kaha to aap ney phir (لا حول wala قوۃ الا باللہ) kaha aur iskey baad isi tarah kaha jis tarah muazzan ney kaha. phir farmaney lagey : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah farmatey suna hai."
679,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab tum muazzan ki aawaz suno to jis tarah wo kahe isi tarah tum bhi kaho phir mujh par durood padho. jo shakhs mujh par eik dafa durood bhejeyga Allah Taala is par das dafa rehmat nazil farmaeyga phir Allah Taala sey merey liye maqame wasila ka sawal karo. ye jannat main eik maqam hai jo Allah Taala key sab bandon mein sey sirf eik bandey key laaiq hai aur mujhey ummid hai ke wo banda main hunga lihaza jo shakhs merey liye maqame wasila ki dua kerega uskey liye meri shafa'at lazim hogi."
680,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shaks muazzan ki Azan suney aur kahe : (أشھد ان لا الہ الا اللہ … … وبمحمد رسولا),''main bhi gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, wo akela hai, us ka koi shareek nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. main Allah ko bator Rab aur Islam ko bator Deen aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bator Rasool pasand karta hun.'' to uskey gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
681,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Azan sun'ney key baad ye kahe : (اللھم ! رب ھذہ الدعوۃ … … … وابعثہ مقاما محمودا الذی وعدتہ), ''aey Allah ! is mukammal dawat aur qaaim honey wali namaz key Rab ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (jannat mein) maqame-wasila aur fazilat ata farma aur aap ko maqame-Mehmood par faaiz farma jis ka tu ney un sey wada kar rakha hai.'' uskey liye qiyamat key din meri shafa'at lazim ho gaee."
682,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har do azaanon (Azan aur iqaamat) key darmiyan (nafl) namaz hai. har do azaanon key darmiyan namaz hai. har do azaanon key darmiyan namaz hai, us shakhs key liye jo padhna chahey."
683,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein) jab muazzan (Maghrib ki) Azan kehta to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key bahut sey as-haab uthtey aur namaz padhney key liye jaldi jaldi sutonon ka rukh kartey yahan tak ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif latey to wo us haal mein hotey they, yani Maghrib sey pehley ki sunnatein padh rahey hotey they aur Azan aur iqaamat key darmiyan koi ziyada fasla na hota tha."
684,Hazrat Abu-Shaa'saa sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha jab ke eik aadmi Azan key baad masjid mein sey guzra yahan tak ke masjid sey bahar nikal gaya to Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is shakhs ney Hazrat Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki hai.
685,Hazrat Abu Shaa'saa sey manqul (naqalhui) hai ke eik aadmi namaz ki Azan key baad masjid sey nikla to Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is shakhs ney Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki hai.
686,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki namaz sey faraaghat key baad sey Fajr tulu honey tak giyara rakat padhtey they. har do rakaaton par salam phertey aur aakhir main eik rakat alag padhtey aur itna (lambaa) sajda kartey ke tum mein sey koi shakhs pachas aayaat padh sakta tha. phir sar uthatey. phir jab muazzan Fajr ki Azan sey farigh hota aur aap ko Fajr nazar aaney lagti to aap do halki rakatein (subah ki sunnat) padhtey phir apney daeyn pehlu par let jatey yahan tak ke muazzan aap ko iqaamat ki ittilaa deney aata. phir aap uskey sath nikal jatey. Imam Zohri key shagrid is hadees key bayan mein lafzi taur par eik doosrey sey kami-beshi kartey hain.
687,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key azad karda ghulam Kureb sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki namaz kaisi thi? to unhoney bataya ke aap ney witr samet giyara rakat padhein phir aap so gaey yahan tak ke aap ko (gehri) neend aa gaee. mainey aap ko khar'raatey bhartey dekha. phir aap key paas Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai. aap uthey aur do rakatein (sunnate-Fajr) padhein phir logon ko namaz padhaai. (naya) wuzu nahin kiya.
688,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab iqaamat ho jaey to khadey na huwa karo yahan tak ke mujhey aata huwa dekh lo."
